{"tid":1408513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[各區正式撚狗] 街坊如果見狗多 上一上樓先 兩個鐘後再落街 loop!","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:08:00.000Z","uid":231206,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c451824549bb9ce50726c4072dd05a812912639d","tid":1408513,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:32.000Z","msg":"黃大仙宜家好多狗 上樓飲啖茶再落黎<br />\n呢個就係自己區嘅好處 散完可以<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時集結</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n瘋狂撚狗! 班狗又要坐車 又要搞一大輪上哂gear先黎<br />\n<br />\n我地就街坊黎嘅 日日落去都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次一有狗黎 即刻上樓 等2-3個鐘再落街就得<br />\n<br />\n到時睇你班傻狗走唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗唔走就由佢地罰企 引哂啲警力企係到 其他區嘅壓力就少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果班狗走 就兩個鐘頭後再落街<br />\n到時你班傻狗咪上多次裝 坐車黎黃大仙比人撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔止黃大仙 全港所有區嘅街坊都可以咁<br />\n<br />\n宜家遍地開花 <br />\n各區狗屋係無咁多本區警力守到 <br />\n要清狗屋係<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要靠增援</span> <br />\n大家可以隨便撚果班坐車遊走嘅防暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cada74228c6c2b4559f84d9e2e561d506d332b","tid":1408513,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"無限輪迴就得 我地只係屋企落樓下<br />\n而班狗就要上裝 坐車黎增援<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ba987731e5e37813d2f655adf1ba4ea567d457","tid":1408513,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"有狗黎增援 隨時返屋企飲杯野 涼下冷氣<br />\n落兩個鐘再落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f3963db6793cbb6587e911a6fa6ef17f4fa15d","tid":1408513,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:37:58.000Z","msg":"到時班狗都唔知黎唔黎好<br />\n陣間坐車黎到又要full gear 成身汗咁睇街坊上樓涼冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d3413bef5c1fc2f7211ae92111ba56ed8d1178","tid":1408513,"uid":41576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e98ed99cdd11b6acb83cc1b56e314ac6831dd4e","tid":1408513,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"請統一口徑！！！<br />\n唔好用偏激、嘩眾取寵既做法<br />\n一定要客觀而且清晰列出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用字好重要，否則只會令人覺得你只係洩憤同作大<br />\n請準確地列出所犯罪行<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位文宣手足！！"},{"pid":"215a1fab51a759c47287ba47fdebd225924a2106","tid":1408513,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54558c878a46ec7de680bb0afca09886b3c73b7","tid":1408513,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"重推一下"},{"pid":"11b2c019109a2fa5af85599a0d1595ff06e4af2e","tid":1408513,"uid":271974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}